*Nestane* mu je nadu. (He lost hope.)
Svi su nestali. (*Nestali* are all gone.)
On je *nestao* u planinama. (He disappeared in the mountains.)
Moje sreće je *nestalo*. (My happiness has disappeared.)
Ona je *nestala* u večeri. (She disappeared in the evening.)
*Nestalo* je vremena. (Time has run out.)